Acceptance: bundles can represent tool policy, codebase grants, memory scopes, credential refs, MCP/skill refs, domain refs, and instruction layers without exposing secret values. Existing room profile fields compile into an implicit legacy bundle. Config parse/validation tests cover duplicate bundle IDs and invalid references. Likely files: runtime_config_types.ml, runtime_config.ml, config_loader.ml, access_bundle.ml, tests.